These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-1::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, bongani, havana, oliveros, dunhill, bolivar
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: classical, house, jazz, r&b, rock, soul
 1. the fan of jazz is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
 2. the bongani-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
 3. the bongani-smoker is somewhere to the right of the fan of classical##5
 4. the fan of soul is not to the left of the havana-smoker##8
 5. the bolivar-smoker is somewhere to the right of the fan of rock##5
 6. the fan of rock is somewhere between the fan of jazz and the bolivar-smoker##7
 7. the tiparillo-smoker is not to the left of the fan of jazz##8
 8. the dunhill-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
 9. the bolivar-smoker is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker##3
10. the fan of classical is not to the left of the oliveros-smoker##8
11. the fan of rock is somewhere to the right of the oliveros-smoker##5
12. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
13. the havana-smoker is somewhere to the right of the fan of jazz##5
14. the bolivar-smoker is somewhere between the fan of house and the havana-smoker##7
15. the fan of soul is somewhere to the right of the fan of classical##5
16. the dunhill-smoker is not the fan of r&b##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |   4   |       5        |   6   |
| Cigar           | oliveros | bongani | tiparillo | dunhill | bolivar | havana |
| Music-Genre   | classical | jazz    | house  | rock  | r&b            | soul  |

