.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-3::.
There are 6 different nationalities: american, argentine, british, canadian, polish, spanish
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, prince, game, dunhill, oliveros, fonseca
 1. the prince-smoker is somewhere to the left of the british##5
 2. the argentine is somewhere to the right of the prince-smoker##5
 3. the fonseca-smoker is somewhere to the right of the polish##5
 4. the game-smoker is not to the left of the argentine##8
 5. the british is somewhere to the left of the fonseca-smoker##5
 6. the spanish is on the left or right of the british##3
 7. the vegafina-smoker is somewhere to the right of the british##5
 8. the canadian is not to the right of the canadian##8
 9. the american is somewhere to the right of the british##5
10. the dunhill-smoker is on the far right##1
11. the fonseca-smoker is somewhere between the polish and the game-smoker##7
12. the prince-smoker is somewhere to the left of the game-smoker##5
13. the spanish is between the oliveros-smoker and the fonseca-smoker##2
14. the argentine is on the right of the canadian##1
15. the game-smoker is somewhere between the fonseca-smoker and the american##7
16. the oliveros-smoker is not to the left of the oliveros-smoker##8
17. the fonseca-smoker is somewhere to the right of the oliveros-smoker##5
18. the polish is the prince-smoker##1
19. the game-smoker is not the american##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |       4       |     5     |    6     |
