.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-4::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: march, february, november, august, october, july
The people have 6 different hobbies: card-games, drawing, magic-tricks, reading, woodworking, writing
 1. the person who's hobby is reading is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##8
 2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##5
 3. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's birthday is in march##2
 4. the person who's birthday is in august is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in october and the person who's hobby is drawing##7
 6. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##8
 9. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##5
10. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5
11. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##5
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere between the person who's hobby is writing and the person who's birthday is in july##7
13. the person who's hobby is writing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
14. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
15. the person who's hobby is writing is in an even position##4
16. the person who's birthday is in november is in an even position##4
17. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |      2      |     3      |    4    |      5       |      6      |
| Birthday    | march | july    | october     | august  | february    | november |
| Hobby   | drawing  | woodworking | card-games | writing | magic-tricks | reading     |

