 3. the person drinking 7up is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
 5. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person drinking tea##1
 6. the person drinking juice is not to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##8
 7. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 8. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
 9. the person who's hobby is video-games is not to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##8
10. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
11. the person drinking juice is not the person who's hobby is board-games##6
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
13. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
14. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
15. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

