The people prefer 6 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, funk, gospel, r&b, rock
 1. the person playing bridge is somewhere between the fan of r&b and the fan of funk##7
 2. the person playing whist is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
 3. the fan of r&b is not to the left of the person playing domino##8
 4. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the left of the fan of classical##5
 5. the person playing bridge is between the person playing mah-jongg and the fan of funk##2
 6. the fan of dubstep is somewhere between the person playing whist and the fan of funk##7
 7. the person playing domino is somewhere to the left of the fan of rock##5
 8. the fan of rock is not to the right of the person playing scrabble##8
 9. the person playing bridge is somewhere between the person playing scrabble and the person playing mah-jongg##7
10. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
11. the person playing domino is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4     |   5   |   6    |
| Game      | whist    | go | domino | mah-jongg       | bridge | scrabble |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | dubstep  | r&b      | classical | rock  | funk   |

