 2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
 4. the person drinking juice is somewhere between the owner of the horse and the person drinking lemonade##7
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person drinking juice is between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking 7up##2
 7. the owner of the turtle is not to the right of the person drinking 7up##8
 8. the owner of the turtle is not to the left of the owner of the goat##8
 9. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
10. the owner of the horse is not the person drinking soy-milk##6
11. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
12. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
13. the owner of the horse is not to the left of the owner of the cat##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |     4      |     5     |    6     |
| Beverage   | lemonade | almond-milk | 7up  | juice     | sprite | soy-milk |
| Pet           | cat        | goat    | turtle | chinchilla | horse     | hamster  |

